# task-sidebar — environment variables
# Copy to `.env` and customize, or export in your shell.

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# VAULT_ROOT — absolute path to your PARA-structured Obsidian-style vault.
#
# Defaults to `./sample-vault` (resolved from cwd) when unset, so `pnpm dev`
# works out of the box against the bundled demo. Point at your own vault
# once you've verified the sample works.
#
# Required shape: VAULT_ROOT/1-Projects/<slug>/{README.md, tasks.md, tasks/*.md}
# See docs/DATA-MODEL.md for the full layout + frontmatter schema.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# VAULT_ROOT=/Users/you/vault

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Optional life-os companion scripts.
#
# Leave unset to run task-sidebar standalone. When unset:
#   - Tasks surface with `priority: null` (unranked chip in UI)
#   - Done-transitions stay local (no parent-goal rollup)
#
# To enable, set to absolute paths of the Python scripts. See docs/LIFE-OS.md
# for where to obtain them and what they do.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# PRIORITY_SCRIPT_PATH=/path/to/life-os/scripts/priority_infer.py
# RECONCILE_SCRIPT_PATH=/path/to/life-os/scripts/status_reconcile.py

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# PORT — HTTP listener port for the combined Vite+Express dev server.
# Defaults to 5174.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# PORT=5174
